==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Tumulate
<hw>Tu"mu*late</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>tumulatus</ets>, p. p. of <ets>tumulare</ets> to tumulate. See
<er>Tumulus</er>.]</ety> <def>To cover, as a corpse, with a mound or
tomb; to bury.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Tumulate</ent>⟦br⟧

